{"TopicId":221328,"ForumId":144,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal\u0027s helmet clips through the bottom of 1.25m capsule [Mk1 \u0022Tin Can\u0022 Command Pod]","CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-19T20:50:21Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-19T20:50:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Win10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0i710700K | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0RTX2060 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs it says. Best seen when decelerating, as the force gets applied to the Kerbal.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002220231219200425_1.jpg.d4df5d36ac7f983158823c21e431beca.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/uploads/monthly_2023_12/20231219200425_1.jpg.d4df5d36ac7f983158823c21e431beca.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-12-29T15:02:46Z\u0022 title=\u002212/29/2023 03:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Dec 29\u0022\u003EDecember 29, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Spicat\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KUAR","CreatedById":229322,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-19T23:21:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have also seen this bug\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wefightforpeace","CreatedById":199098,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T02:21:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis bug is present in 0.2 as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JeanRenaud","CreatedById":176915,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T04:37:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI confirm, seen it too. 0.2.0.0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Doorjelly","CreatedById":231612,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T05:12:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalso seen this, noticed especially when parachute deploys\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WhereAreTheBathrooms","CreatedById":167730,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T16:38:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 10 Home 64-bit (10.0, Build 19045) | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD Ryzen 7 7800X3D 8-Core Processor | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4090 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32768MB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESeverity: \u003C/strong\u003EMedium, no workaround, jsut seems to happen sometimes depending on Kerbonaut\u0027s animations\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EFrequency:\u003C/strong\u003E Happens every few seconds in flight, most noticeable on re-entry as this is when the heatshield is exposed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDescription:\u003C/strong\u003E In flight, when a HS-125 Heatshield is attached to a Mk1 \u0022Tin Can\u0022 Command Pod containing a brave Kerbonaut, the Kerbonaut will occasionally perform animations within the command pod which cause the back of their helmet to clip through the heatshield, becoming partially visible from the outside camera\u0027s perspective. Unclear whether this occurs without the heatshield too, or if the presense of the heatshield is causing the clipping to show where it otherwise would not.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/uploads/monthly_2023_12/Untitled.png.e75eacc131ba85cebafb1c5a468bd37c.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ipslightbox=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/cfield.php?storage=form_Fields\u0026amp;path=CarouselI.json\u0026amp;fileKey=[!AES128GCM[e%2B2tbEYAw2SGI8MfuDiC8HkSfP%2BaxTqDcLEQOyyhOelRCxN0Pc95ZxcSaNnCnNSWxdYl76SIRkUxbal0/wbW][013e05fe3f0e688b9a2d18e7][9004f43cc53eeca5d50f79149c7cb5ab]]\u0022\u003ECarouselI.json\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cstyle type=\u0022text/css\u0022\u003E\r\n.ipsImage {\r\nwidth: 900px !important;\r\n}\u003C/style\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"uglyduckling81","CreatedById":129740,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T17:53:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224349004\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022221328\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221703049168\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022231612\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Doorjelly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, Doorjelly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalso seen this, noticed especially when parachute deploys\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Kerbals also block the window with the top of their head in the starter capsule after an EVA. So you can only see the top of their helmet through the little window whilst also seeing their helmet poking out the bottom of the capsule.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Space Peacock","CreatedById":224498,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T18:13:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/167730-wherearethebathrooms/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167730\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/167730-wherearethebathrooms/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@WhereAreTheBathrooms\u003C/a\u003E merged your report\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GalacticPresidentSuperstar","CreatedById":228656,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T22:48:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 11 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Intel(R) Core(TM) i9-9900K CPU | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2060 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E63.8 GB Available / 64 GB Total\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWas playing some ksp 2 and I saw that my kerbal\u0027s head was sticking out of the capsule a bit. I dont have a heat shield so it doesnt cover it up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/uploads/monthly_2023_12/20231220154330_1.jpg.cfb377a1ab2b6d2c40f0c7fe09886e48.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ipslightbox=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cstyle type=\u0022text/css\u0022\u003E\r\n.ipsImage {\r\nwidth: 900px !important;\r\n}\u003C/style\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Space Peacock","CreatedById":224498,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T22:57:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/228656-galacticpresidentsuperstar/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022228656\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/228656-galacticpresidentsuperstar/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@GalacticPresidentSuperstar\u003C/a\u003E merged your report\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robin217","CreatedById":231862,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-29T03:49:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 11 Home Single Language 64-bit (10.0, Build 22621) | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A013th Gen Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-13700HX (24 CPUs), ~2.1GHz | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4060 Laptop GPU | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E16\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is something I have noticed twice so far (I have played KSP2 only for it about an hour so far).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSometimes during the flight, due to some movements of the Kerbals, their body clips through the vehicle . It didn\u0027t affect the flight in any way but it did look weird.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the attached image I noticed this during the reentry from the Kerbin orbit.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe other time i noticed this was on the launch-pad where the Kerbal clipped through the vehicle, during one of their idle animations.\u00A0 Sadly I do not have a image for it as it happened only for a moment and I couldn\u0027t capture it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/uploads/monthly_2023_12/Screenshot2023-12-28224612.png.59f7f0a4b3bce1d9627882a6fb97260e.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ipslightbox=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cstyle type=\u0022text/css\u0022\u003E\r\n.ipsImage {\r\nwidth: 900px !important;\r\n}\u003C/style\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-29T15:03:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/231862-robin217/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022231862\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/231862-robin217/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Robin217\u003C/a\u003E, merged your bug report.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}